column5: Udon Bird Sanctuary ("Friendly, comfortable, small, real-world-analogous, uses your hands for that VR-essential feeling of embodiment.")
Particles (Music Visualizer) ("Show them something VRChat does really well: electronic music with flying colors. Then tell them about VRChat's amazing rave scene.")
Shader Clay Sculpting ("Some more hands-on interaction. Tell them about creating studio art in VR, and tell them about @VermillionVR while you're at it.")
[Environment][Calm Comfort] Sakura Island ("Show them some wonder and imagination with a dose of surreal.")
Star Size Comparison ("Now that wonder is on the table, show them VR's potential to supplement education; use 3D presence to make them feel the scale of stars and planets.")
[Musicmaking] Musical Flowers ("Chill for a minute with some more hands-on good vibes.")
Just Paint and Chill ("Do some more art. 2D this time.")
[Explore & Imagine] Steps of the Campanula - カンパニュラの足音 ("Now that you're grounded a bit more, time to get surreal again.")
Putt Putt Quest ("..and that's enough exploring VRChat to start. Time to play a game. Mini-golf is the perfect low-intensity easy-pace place to start.")

[Hangout] Sovren's Chill home ("Finally, if you made it this far, relax and debrief in any of the dozens of cozy Quest-compatible hangout worlds. Make a private instance of something good in the Hot or  Spotlight row.")
[Explore & Imagine][Eye Candy & Sound] Lunar Capital ("This and below entries are on @jokerispunk's spreadsheet--but not the Twitter thread--as bonus ideas!")
[Musicmaking] MARIMBURE ｜ Marimba ｜ マリンバ ｜ MARIMBURE（メルのシアター）
[Environment] A D R I F T
[Big Hangout] Spirits of the Sea 海の幽霊
